Hello and thank you for your interest in our vehicles!
Mariya and I are very excited to help you have a safe, productive and fun trip whether it is for business or pleasure. 
We try to be very flexible with our customers and appreciate your reciprocity. 
Thank you for your support and kind reviews which we hope are helpful to our new customers!  
We look forward to seeing you when you come to the Chicagoland area.

And don't forget to check out our vehicle line-up of over 20 vehicles!

Some include:  Tesla Model 3, Mitsubishi Outlander (7 passengers), GMC Acadia (7 passengers), Mini Cooper S and Fiat 500. 

Regards, 

Mariya and Eric

Hi everyone. 
I am Mike, nice to meet you. I am an engineer by my education so I really like cars. Proud owner of my 2020 Mercedes S Class and 2020 Ducati Panigale, yep, years are just a coincidence. I can drive everything that has wheels, cars, motorcycles, forklifts, semi-trucks, you name it. 
My passions are motorcycles, airplanes and traveling; if I could, I would invest all my time in them.  Unfortunately I can't do that since I own a trucking company with 20 semis in it, so all my time is dedicated to work.

Welcome to our Turo host profile! At Chicago Premier Rentals, we are proud to offer top-notch customer service and make your rental experience as smooth and enjoyable as possible. Our location near O'Hare Airport makes us an ideal choice for travelers looking for a convenient and hassle-free rental experience.

We understand that renting a car can come with a lot of rules and restrictions, which is why we've made it our mission to keep things simple and straightforward. With us, you won't have to worry about any inconvenient rules during or after your trip. Our goal is to make your rental experience as seamless and stress-free as possible.

In addition to our commitment to customer service, we also have extensive experience with different electric vehicles (EVs). Whether you're looking for a stylish and eco-friendly Hyundai Ionic 5 or a luxurious Audi E-tron, we've got you covered. Our extensive knowledge of EVs means that we can provide you with a top-notch rental experience, complete with helpful tips and tricks for getting the most out of your rental.

We have everything from powerful and efficient EVs to luxurious gas vehicles, so you can find the perfect rental for your needs.

All our vehicles are well optioned out and come with AWD.

Book with us today and experience the ultimate rental experience in the heart of the Windy City!
